;
;    5. Set C = m + 2^M * e
;
;    6. If S=1, set msb of C = s.
;
;    The algorithms that I (GH) remember were used on the Electron Isotope Spectrometers (E..C.Stone, PI) that flew on IMPs 7 and 8,
